chat.msg: hola, q tal? ready to play?
si
awesome! i'm at the starting point right now, next to a twig leading to a small island
where should i go?
ve hacia la girafa
there's no direct path from here to the giraffe
should i go to the tiger's island first?
yes
Muy bien, ¡cruza la ramita para llegar a la isla del tigre! ¿ahora que?
cruza la ramita hacia la mariposa
there is no direct twig to the butterfly from here
Should I go through the parrot first?
yes
¡excelente! Ahora estoy junto al loro en la isla grande.
¿que sigue?
cruza la piedra hacia la rana
ready! here I am, on frog island
where to now?
go back to the elephant
Vale amigo, estoy al lado del elefante otra vez.
cruza la rama hacia la girafa
done, now standing right next to the giraffe
what's next?
cruza la rama hacia la serpiente
done! i'm next to the snake
where to now?
hacia el tesoro
awesome! i took 2 steps east and reached the treasure
*finished* was that the correct path?
hola, q tal? ready to go?
si
awesome! let's get moving! first, take a few steps to the left, just below the bench nearby
you'll cross a little trail. see that florist stand? head towards it but don't go all the way
ya
nice! as soon as you're near, take a sharp u-turn to the left, cross back over the trail, and start heading back towards our fluffy white friend
can you see the dog from there?
si
great job! now, cross over the branch towards the south
keep heading straight down the map. remember to watch your steps!
creo que ya lo hice
I'm impressed! see that other white dog by the picnic blanket? keep heading towards it but don't step over the blanket
'kay?
ok
¡magnífico! Una vez que estés cerca de la manta de picnic, haz un círculo alrededor de ella, tocando el cuenco de bayas y luego comienza a dirigirte hacia el oeste.
Suena como una aventura genial, ¿verdad?
si
super! then you'll come across another wooden branch
use it to cross the river again, this time heading north. can you see it?
si
good job! once you've made it across the river, spot the green bush on your path. it's a tricky one, so make sure not to touch it
instead, circle it from the right. cool?
ya
you're doing awesome! now, see the florist's stand in front of you? keep going until you reach it
ya
perfect! Your next move is to the left (west), under the flower shop until you find a large bridge.
Do you see the two people on bicycles? you have to go through there. Are you still with me?
ya
fantastic! continue past the bridge
you'll see two elderly folks reading newspapers on a bench just ahead
si
great! now move a bit to the south between the kind old folks and another wooden branch you see nearby
los veo
nicely done! next up is a green bush
it's right next to the end of the branch you just passed. can you spot it?
si
wonderful! now, move to your right, between the branch and the bush
hey there, estas listo?
si
awesome! i'm at the tent right now, right up north
how should i proceed?
yes, walk straight and pass the dog
Muy bien, bailando junto a un perro a la izquierda hacia el fuego.
¿Adónde vamos ahora, amigo?
ve hacia el hongo
yup, ya estoy en el hongo rojo
vas a ver un carro azul, pasalo, youre going to see a bush
ok, pasé el carro, veo el arbusto
¿y ahora qué?
vas a ver un telescope
got ya, aquí estoy en el telescopio azul
vas a ir hacia las piedras, y ahi vas a ver una cabana
just made it to the rocks, i see the house! *finished* you're a great guide, hombre! thanks!
hola, q tal? ready to start?
si
cool! so, you're at the three palm trees, right? move south-west, under the first tree
then swing a right across the next palm tree. turn sharp left just before the third one and head straight to the south
ya
nice! then, look slightly left to avoid that brown puppy we're seeing
then hang a right, back toward the south. you got this!
ya
great! now, head between the big rock on your left and that smaller one on your right, straight towards the ocean
fancy a swim?
ya
alright, mate! once you're in the water, you'll see a red crab
just turn right and go alongside that huge rock. keep heading west, alright?
ya
super! notice the medium-sized rock down your way? keep your line westwards until you reach it
ya
got your attention on a shark, it's time to make a sharp right
doing okay?
i think so
¡excelente! No dejes que esa bola azul, amarilla y blanca te distraiga, regresa a tierra.
evítalo y la roca mediana y comienza a moverte hacia el norte.
ya
excellent! now, take a slight left and move north-west
you should be between a bright red tent on your left and a speaker on your right
ya
sweet! now, just arc around that tent and keep heading south
we're almost there!
ya
awesome, don't go in the water this time! just turn right before hitting the sea and go below the red kayak
ya
now, crank a 90-degree turn to the right and trudge on north along the kayak
ya
chu know what? you made it to the finish! that small green bush over there is your final spot
great job, you!
